<p class="has-text-color has-small-font-size" style="color:#a8b8cd">GreenShift has conditional loading of all assets so there is big chance that you will get 100 score without any caching. But you need to have good hosting with small TTFB and pay attention to your content. We don't recommend to use heavy media in first screen of the site. Also, replace all image files to webp or svg format and avoid using external scripts and heavy plugins</p>
